    {
      "question": "Do you offer design assistance, and how involved can I be in the design process?",
      "answer": "Absolutely! Design is a core part of our service. Our experienced designers are here to guide you through every step of the creative process. We welcome and encourage your active involvement. We start by listening to your ideas, understanding your lifestyle, and assessing your functional needs. We''ll then present material samples, finish options, and hardware selections. Using advanced 2D and 3D rendering software, we''ll bring your vision to life, allowing you to visualize the final product before any work begins. You''ll have opportunities to review, provide feedback, and request revisions until the design perfectly matches your expectations. Our goal is to collaborate closely with you to create cabinetry that is both beautiful and highly functional."
