s straight and flush, even on imperfect surfaces. While it may require a bit more time and precision, we strive to achieve a beautiful, professional finish regardless of minor inconsistencies in your home''s structure."}]}', updated_at = '2026-02-17T19:49:35.481Z' WHERE id = 'oZuvw2cmXVEG2lmegUtO7';
