UPDATE page_sections SET content = '{"title": "Epoxy Floor Coating: Professional Tips for Homeowners", "tips": ["**Vet Your Contractor Thoroughly:** Before hiring, research licensed and insured professionals with a proven track record in epoxy flooring. Look for positive reviews, a strong portfolio of completed projects, and ask for references to ensure their expertise.", "**Understand Epoxy Types & Surface Prep:** Not all epoxy is created equal (e.g., 100% solids for maximum durability). Inquire about the specific type of epoxy they plan to use and, critically, their surface preparation process (e.g., concrete grinding, crack repair), as proper prep is vital for adhesion and longevity.", "**Get Detailed, Comparative Quotes:** Obtain at least three written quotes. Ensure each quote clearly specifies the type of epoxy, number of coats, detailed surface preparation steps, estimated timeline, and warranty information. Be wary of bids that are significantly lower than others.", "**Ensure Proper Ventilation & Temperature Control:** During application, epoxy fumes can be strong. Confirm the professional has a plan for adequate ventilation. Also, ideal temperature and humidity are crucial for proper curing; discuss how they manage these environmental factors.", "**Clarify Curing Times & Restricted Access:** Understand the precise walk-on and drive-on curing times. Respect these periods strictly to prevent damage to the newly applied coating, and plan your access to the coated area accordingly.", "**Follow Post-Installation Care Instructions:** Ask your contractor for specific cleaning and maintenance guidelines. Using recommended cleaners and avoiding harsh chemicals or abrasive tools will significantly extend the life and maintain the pristine appearance of your epoxy floor.", "**Understand Your Warranty:** Carefully review the warranty agreement provided by your contractor. Know what types of defects or issues are covered, for how long, and what actions (or inactions) might void the warranty. Keep all documentation in a safe place."]}', updated_at = '2026-02-17T19:51:07.909Z' WHERE id = 'aCUzCor1dS9GDj4xXZwlF';
