UPDATE page_sections SET content = '{"content": {
  "title": "Transform Your Home: Expert Countertop Installation Made Easy",
  "text": "Thinking about updating your kitchen or bathroom? New countertops are often the centerpiece, dramatically transforming the look and feel of your space. More than just a surface, they''re an investment in both aesthetics and functionality. But with so many options and the precision required, professional installation is key to ensuring a flawless finish and lasting durability.\n\nFrom luxurious granite and elegant quartz to versatile laminate and rustic butcher block, the choices are endless. Each material offers unique benefits in terms of style, maintenance, and longevity. While DIY might seem tempting, countertop installation is a complex job that requires specialized tools, precise measurements, and expert handling, especially for heavy or delicate materials. A professional ensures proper leveling, seamless seams, accurate cuts for sinks and cooktops, and secure installation, preventing costly mistakes down the line.\n\n**What to Expect & Practical Advice:**\n*   **Planning & Selection:** Before any work begins, you''ll consult with your ProBuddy professional to discuss material options, edge profiles, backsplash choices, and your budget. They can guide you through the pros and cons of each material to find the perfect fit for your lifestyle.\n*   **Precise Measurement:** This is where professionals shine. They''ll take incredibly precise measurements of your existing cabinets, accounting for any irregularities, ensuring your new countertops fit perfectly.\n*   **Old Countertop Removal (if applicable):** Your ProBuddy team can handle the careful removal and disposal of your old countertops, minimizing disruption and ensuring a clean slate for the new installation.\n*   **Fabrication & Installation:** Once your chosen material is fabricated to your exact specifications, our skilled installers will meticulously place and secure your new countertops. This includes cutting openings for sinks, faucets, and cooktops on-site if necessary, and ensuring all seams are expertly joined and sealed.\n*   **Cleanup & Final Walkthrough:** After installation, the area will be thoroughly cleaned, and your professional will conduct a final walkthrough with you, explaining any care instructions and ensuring your complete satisfaction.\n\nWhile installation itself can often be completed in a day or two depending on the complexity and material, the entire process from selection to fabrication can take a few weeks. Expect some noise and dust during removal and installation, but our professionals strive to minimize disruption and maintain a tidy workspace.\n\nReady to give your home the stunning upgrade it deserves? Let ProBuddy connect you with top-rated countertop installation experts who will bring your vision to life with precision, care, and quality craftsmanship. Get started today and enjoy a beautiful, functional new space!"
}}', updated_at = '2026-02-17T19:52:23.709Z' WHERE id = 'iqbT_HdqtiMuNyEfcLgQB';
UPDATE page_sections SET content = '{"faq": {
