      "answer": "ProBuddy professionals are skilled in installing a wide variety of countertop materials to suit diverse tastes and budgets. Common materials include natural stone (granite, marble, quartzite), engineered stone (quartz), solid surface, laminate, butcher block, and concrete. Each material has unique properties, benefits, and installation requirements, and our experts can guide you in choosing the best option for your home."
