                "answer": "Several factors impact the total cost of deck or porch repair. These include the extent of the damage (minor vs. major structural issues), the type and quality of materials chosen for the repair (e.g., pressure-treated wood vs. composite), the complexity of the repair, labor costs, accessibility to the work area, and whether any permits are required. Getting a detailed quote from a ProBuddy professional is the best way to understand the specific costs for your project."
